{"tid":494622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"梅毒感染者激增　日本議員咎責「支那人」","createTime":"2017-12-09T19:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T10:17:39.000Z","uid":47714,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"33779ae61c7e114d3383d9cc120b4a2b05bf8a75","tid":494622,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T19:53:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=6630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6630&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO24zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e0fc96e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=6630</a><br />\n<br />\n日本國立感染研究所日前（11月28日）公佈，今年梅毒感染人數逾5000人，也是1973年來最嚴重的感染情況。東京都葛飾區的地方議員鈴木信行，在得悉此消息後，馬上在Twitter發表見解，直指「支那人」是日本梅毒患者人數增加的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://amd.c.yimg.jp/amd/20171208-00010002-yomidr-001-1-view.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Famd.c.yimg.jp%2Famd%2F20171208-00010002-yomidr-001-1-view.jpg&h=0d392324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鈴木信行在Twitter上分享梅毒感染人數的報導時，在帖文寫著「到底是誰帶來日本的，可想而知是訪日人數最多的外國人，就是支那人啊！梅毒感染者，今年超過5000人，睽違44年&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n不只是Twitter，鈴木更在網誌上引用一名醫師的文章，指出近十年來訪日中國人的增加速率與梅毒感染的增加速率成正比，所以一切都是中國人的錯。他在接受《西日本新聞》的訪問時解釋，「中國稱國內有數十萬梅毒患者，因此絕對會有傳染途徑。為了守護從事性工作的日本女性，我身為議員當然要做出警告。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.news.livedoor.com/newsimage/stf/3/4/34686_1497_bfe97b9e77142fa8f9de7c8074bf212a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.news.livedoor.com%2Fnewsimage%2Fstf%2F3%2F4%2F34686_1497_bfe97b9e77142fa8f9de7c8074bf212a.jpg&h=8926c2bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，日本國立感染研究所以及厚生勞動省均否認鈴木信行的說法，表示目前無法證實梅毒感染人數激增與中國觀光客有關，須要進一步調查釐清。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2277336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2277336&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO24zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3f1e42bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2277336&h=8f457ad2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2277336</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本國立感染研究所日前公布，今年梅毒感染人數逾5000人，也是1973年來最嚴重的感染情況。對此，東京葛飾區議員鈴木信行（Suzuki Nobuyuki）於推特上，直接點名與外來的中國人脫不了干係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpj2tQj6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpj2tQj6.jpg&h=e1680369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpJBg9hz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpJBg9hz.jpg&h=d3bcd002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，鈴木信行在文中提到，為什麼今年梅毒感染者眾多，可想而知，應與赴日人數最多的外國觀光客，即支那人有關。鈴木信行也於部落格引用一篇文章，指出10年來赴日遊玩人數急遽攀升，與梅毒感染增加速度具有一致性，其中中國人最多，因此推測國人染上梅毒，主要是「支那人」害的。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，對於鈴木信行以「支那人」一詞稱呼中國人，有人覺得不尊重，認為其言論內容已涉及種族歧視。鈴木信行駁斥，中國稱國內有數十萬名梅毒感染者，赴日的話很有可能是傳染途徑，為保護國內從事性工作的女子，身為議員當然有義務提出警告，且「用支那、中國有差嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，不過，掌管醫療、勞動與社會福利的厚生勞動省、發布數據的日本國立感染研究所均否認鈴木信行的說法，澄清日本感染梅毒人數激增的原因，目前無法證實與中國觀光客有關，仍須進一步調查釐清。"},{"pid":"ff76bfd2e332380972fd2b7676ba48100a92b826","tid":494622,"uid":44956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T21:00:59.000Z","msg":"咁都關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0e08738ec701e911ca43be7501992940fccc2a","tid":494622,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T21:01:14.000Z","msg":"性病抗日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312df05d38c72081b9c023fa50ec754c607fd924","tid":494622,"uid":96146,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:35:29.000Z","msg":"生性病都可以屈落大陸仔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ba7c82862907da26d0acfb80eb1d8e0fd59602","tid":494622,"uid":81202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:42:31.000Z","msg":"乜佢地啲無料案內所唔係唔接受外國遊客咩<br />\n雖然人在日本  覺得佢地已經唔理"},{"pid":"b533a83842551ba0e5fda762298259ba341419f3","tid":494622,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:57:22.000Z","msg":"藉口黎姐，擺明覺得係時候要限制劣等人種前往日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5e04beb63fef512820bd2a36215b7eee963452","tid":494622,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T23:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜佢地啲無料案內所唔係唔接受外國遊客咩<br />\n雖然人在日本  覺得佢地已經唔理</blockquote><br />\n除左案內所介紹。仲會直接衝入去"},{"pid":"54c1341ce6f3c5a9a08d338263d35c3afafc1c5c","tid":494622,"uid":107231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"可以用支付寶咪track到囉"},{"pid":"d3494b6f2a970075d54cb2c7f95c5fdf6b8e831e","tid":494622,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以用支付寶咪track到囉</blockquote><br />\n突破盲腸"},{"pid":"442b2ff77f4e42bdc5c24545f07e0db74eeee875","tid":494622,"uid":51411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"雖然自己平時乜鳩都鐘意賴落支那人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但見到佢咁樣亂鳩咁屈支那人 忍唔住笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}